dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2019.[This data layer is a centerline Personal Geodatabase Feature Class of the roads in Marinette County. Data is referenced to the Marinette County Coordinate System, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
